data.description:
New reduced price!! Welcome to your charming 2-bed, 1-bath haven in the heart of Debary, Florida! Nestled inthe midst of Central Florida's allure, this home boasts not only a fantastic location butalso solid construction with strong bones. This home is conveniently located only 45minutes from the beach, and 30 minutes from Orlando.Step into a welcoming open floor plan adorned with sleek tile flooring throughout,creating a seamless and modern aesthetic. The newly installed air conditioning ensurescomfort year-round, promising a cool retreat on warm Florida days.One of the highlights of this property is its generous backyard - a spacious oasis whereyou can relax and entertain under the Florida sun. Imagine weekend gatherings,
gardening ventures, or simply enjoying the tranquility of your private outdoor space.
Situated in a quiet community, this residence offers a peaceful retreat from the hustle
and bustle, providing a serene atmosphere for you to call home. Don't miss the
opportunity to make it your own!
